                    <span>We recently moved from Informix to Sql 2K and found this book very useful.  Thanks to this and Henderson's book we were able to make the migration in 6 months.  We actually unplugged the Informix server yesterday.<p>This book teaches how Sql works inside.  The product docs don't even tell half the story, so a book like this can help fill in the gaps.</span>
                  
              
